EN: You have left the area of Room Capure. Please return to the calibrated area to continue the experience.
ZH_CN: 你已经离开MR标定的空间区域，请返回标定区域内继续完成体验

EN: This will save room capture, theme, and spatial anchors (ball drop slides) and exit
ZH_CN: 保存房间标定，房间主题，以及小球滑道锚点数据，并退出应用

EN: Patterned Wall and Celling, Oak Flooring
ZH_CN: 花纹墙面和天花板，橡木地板

EN: Stripped Wall, Wooden Celling, Redwood Flooring
ZH_CN: 条纹墙面，木质天花板，红木地板
透明材质，可以用于测试

EN: Welcome to the New MR Horizon
Put on PICO, Enter a New MR Horizon.

This sample showcases MR capabilities of the PICO Unity Integration SDK, including video passthrough, spatial calibration, spatial anchors, and more. You can experience use-cases such as room decoration, wall doodling, virtual pet, and shooting games. You can also switch between manual and auto modes for spatial calibration.
Decorate your room with different wall, floor, and ceiling textures. This scene demonstrates a use-case of Room Capture.
ZH_CN: 用不同风格的墙面，地面和天花板来装饰房间吧。这个场景示范了房间标定的一个应用。

EN: Has gravity and collides with the slides
Has gravity and collides with the ball
To be anchored in space for the ball to slide on
ZH_CN: 用于锚定在空间中供小球滑动

EN:
This scene demostrates a ball sliding down a track formed by slides that use Spatial Anchors. You can click on the object menu below to build the ball drop experience. 
 
Trigger: Preview creation
Grip: End experience
Y/B: Delete created items
ZH_CN:
演示小球在空间锚点的滑道上滑落。你可以点击下面的物体在空间中搭建滑道并模拟小球延轨道下落撞击骨牌。

Trigger键: 预览创建
Grip键: 结束体验
Y/B键: 删除创建物品

EN:
This sample demonstrates PICO Integration SDK's Sense Pack capabilities and their applications. 
Click the scenes on the left to experience these MR features:)

To open this menu, press A/X Button
ZH_CN:
本示例演示了 PICO Integration SDK 中 Sense Pack 的能力及应用。
点击左侧菜单中的场景，体验丰富的混合现实（MR）功能吧:) 

按下 A 或 X 键可以打开本菜单。

EN: You can manually mark physical structures such as walls, doors, windows, tables, and sofas in your room for the virtual scene and object interactions.
ZH_CN: 你可以手动将房间中的墙、门窗、桌椅、沙发等标定出来，用于虚拟场景和物体的交互。

EN:
This scene provides several doodle tools. 

Press Trigger to select a tool, Hold B/Y button to paint on the walls.
Joystick Left or Right: Change Color, Grip: Cancel
ZH_CN: 涂鸦工具提供了几种不同种类的工具，你可以选择不同的工具，按住B/Y键来在标定出的墙面上进行涂鸦，通过左右推动摇杆来更改颜色，通过Grip键来取消交互。

EN:
The balloon shooting game generates balloons floating upwards within the calibrated space. Use the gun in your hand to shoot them. 

Trigger: Shoot

Grip: End Game
ZH_CN:
射气球游戏会在标定的空间内生成向上漂浮的气球，你可以使用手中的枪来射击气球。

Trigger键: 射击
Grip键: 结束游戏

EN:
In the virtual world feature, you can use a magic wand to open a virtual world based on the calibrated space and allow virtual pets to enter it.

Trigger: Open/Close Virtual World
Grip: End Experience
ZH_CN:
虚拟世界功能中，可以基于标定的空间使用魔杖打开一个虚拟的世界，并可以让虚拟宠物进入其中。

Trigger键: 打开/关闭虚拟世界
Grip键: 结束体验

EN:
You can use the paintball gun to shoot freely within the space and leave paintings on the wall.

Trigger: Shoot
Grip: End Game
ZH_CN:
彩弹射击功能中，你可以使用彩弹枪在空间中随意射击留下彩弹的印记。

Trigger键: 射击
Grip键: 结束游戏

EN: Press the A/X button to open the main menu.
ZH_CN: 按下 A 或 X 键，打开主菜单

EN: You can play fetch with a virtual pet using the tennis ball, or touch the pet to interact with it.
ZH_CN: 你可以扔出网球让宠物去捡球，也可触摸宠物与其互动。

EN: For PICO 4 Ultra, you can use the new Mesh Scanning mode.
ZH_CN: PICO 4 Ultra 用户可使用新的静默环境网格扫描。如要继续体验其他功能，请在使用后关闭扫描。

EN: Trigger: Create anchor\nGrip: End experience\nY/B: Delete anchor
ZH_CN: Trigger 键: 预览锚点\nGrip 键: 结束体验\nY/B 键: 删除锚点

EN: Save Room Capture, Room Theme, and Spatial Anchors (Ball Drop Slides) data
ZH_CN: 保存房间标定，房间主题，和空间锚点（小球滑道）数据
